    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Prerequisite: 15th level, Pact of the Chain feature</em></p>\n<p>You can cast @Item[YjFiMTVmNGY3M2Nl]{Hold Monster} at will - targeting a <strong>celestial</strong>, <strong>fiend</strong>, or <strong>elemental</strong> - without expending a spell slot or material components.</p>\n<p>You must finish a long rest before you can use this invocation on the same creature again.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>FoundryVTT</strong>: This needs to be manually setup on the Warlock's sheet:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Spell copied to posessor's spell list</li>\n<li>Modify spell to be preperation:&nbsp;<strong>at-will</strong></li>\n<li>Modify the spell to be a 1 per day resource</li>\n<li>Modify the spell details&nbsp;<strong>Activation Condition&nbsp;</strong> to be: ['celestial', \"fiend\", \"elemental\"].includes('@raceOrType')</li>\n</ol>",
